# Do not touch

Never edit, create, or commit any of the following unless the user
explicitly asks for it in the current conversation:

- `node_modules/`, `dist/`, `build/` outputs
- `.vite/` cache
- `package-lock.json` (unless a dependency was intentionally added/updated)
- Local IDE settings (`.claude/settings.local.json`, `.vscode/` user
  settings, etc.)
- Originals in `Images/` and `Images-new/` — these are untouched source
  art. Web copies live in `public/assets/edutic-art/` and are produced by
  the Python scripts in `Images-new/`.
